        @NotNull
public TemplateDeclaration findTemplate​(@NotNull
                                        TemplateDeclarationKey templateDeclaration,
                                        @NotNull
                                        SNodeReference callSite)
        Description copied from interface: TemplateExecutionEnvironment
        Retrieve reusable runtime instance that represents TemplateDeclaration. Clients may keep an instance for subsequent reuse during the same transformation session. This is low-level mechanism for sophisticated use, generated templates (unless they keep instances obtained this way) shall resort to other methods to invoke templates, namely TemplateExecutionEnvironment.callSite(TemplateDeclarationKey,SNodeReference).
        Specified by:
        findTemplate in interface TemplateExecutionEnvironment
        Parameters:
        templateDeclaration - identifies template to load
        callSite - identifies location where invocation happens
        Returns:
        never null, non necessarily exact generated class, might be a decorator that traces uses or reports errors.

      • callSite

        @NotNull
public TemplateCallSite callSite​(@NotNull
                                 TemplateDeclarationKey templateIdentityKey,
                                 @NotNull
                                 SNodeReference callSite)
        Description copied from interface: TemplateExecutionEnvironment
        To invoke templates from another generator. Though given compile-time dependencies between modules, we can instantiate their classes, not all generators are 'compiled' as of this writing, and it's just not possible, let alone it's safe to use an identity key to refer to them. Perhaps, one day, with GPs for template models in place and all template models generated/compiled, we can reference classes directly in all cases.
        Specified by:
        callSite in interface TemplateExecutionEnvironment
        Parameters:
        templateIdentityKey - identity of a template declaration
        callSite - identifies location where invocation happens
        Returns:
        an instance that identifies invocation of a given template at particular template location
